text: The canton of Guéret-1 is an administrative division of the Creuse department, in central France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Guéret.Décret n° 2014-161 du 17 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département de la Creuse It consists of the following communes: #Guéret (partly) #Sainte-Feyre #Saint- Laurent #La Saunière #Savennes ==References== Category:Cantons of Creuse
